00:43:35.100 --> 00:43:38.939
So we're dedicated to making open source tools

00:43:38.939 --> 00:43:41.100
available for data scientists.

00:43:41.100 --> 00:43:43.020
And so everything that we were looking at

00:43:43.739 --> 00:43:45.979
