00:43:56.459 --> 00:44:00.540
the ability to run Python scripts inside of the IDE,

00:44:00.540 --> 00:44:04.139
as well as the reticulate packages capabilities

00:44:04.139 --> 00:44:06.699
for combining the R and Python runtimes.

00:44:07.260 --> 00:44:09.260
For example, the Shiny application

00:44:09.260 --> 00:44:11.500
that was calling Python functions.

00:44:11.500 --> 00:44:14.219
That's all available in the open source ecosystem.

